Andrua cannot be compiled with the Visual Studio compiler as it uses C99

Compiler : 
	Add include path (-l) to GLFW3 include directory

Linker : 

Link Libraries (-l) :
	glfw3dll
	glu32
	opengl32
	kernel32
	user32
	gdi32
	winspool
	shell32
	ole32
	oleaut32
	uuid
	comdlg32
	advapi32

Add GLFW's src to linker search path (-L)

Use C99 (-std=c99)

Tested using MingGW gcc version 4.8.1-4.
Worked using CodeBlocks and Eclipse (CDT).